stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Ideated: Task generated

    Ideated --> Deferred: Blocked by dependency
    Ideated --> Specified: Spec generated

    Deferred --> Specified: Dependency resolved

    Specified --> Executing: Worktree spawned

    Executing --> QAReview: Agent completes work
    Executing --> Failed: Timeout or fatal error

    QAReview --> Approved: All criteria met
    QAReview --> Fixing: Issues identified

    Fixing --> Executing: Fixes applied in worktree
    Fixing --> Failed: Max retries exceeded

    Approved --> Merging: Enter merge queue

    Merging --> Merged: Clean merge to main
    Merging --> Reexecuting: Conflict with main

    Reexecuting --> Executing: New worktree from updated base

    Merged --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]

    note right of Ideated
        194 tasks generated
        from codebase analysis
    end note

    note right of Specified
        91 specs produced
        with acceptance criteria
    end note

    note right of QAReview
        71 QA reports generated
        22% rejection rate pass 1
    end note

    note right of Fixing
        95% approval rate
        on second submission
    end note
